subject: Add multi-user support
commitMessage:
Add multi-user support

/opt/usr/voice/ purpose was to stock user's downloaded engines and
associated settings. It has been moved to ~/.voice/ to respect the
multi-user architecture.

Also set valid group and licence tags.

Change-Id: Id87fbf0e0a5baa4534cc65f8e7672991c717dfa8
Bug-Tizen: PTREL-297
Signed-off-by: Kévin THIERRY <kevin.thierry@open.eurogiciel.org>
